{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":9553,"text":"When I was 14 years old,"},{"time":12643,"text":"I had low self-esteem."},{"time":14630,"text":"I felt I was not talented at anything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19314,"text":"One day, I bought a yo-yo."},{"time":23533,"text":"When I tried my first trick,\nit looked like this:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":28771,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":33553,"text":"I couldn't even do the simplest trick,"},{"time":36355,"text":"but it was very natural for me,"},{"time":38696,"text":"because I was not dextrous,\nand hated all sports."},{"time":43561,"text":"But after one week of practicing,"},{"time":46322,"text":"my throws became more like this:"},{"time":54585,"text":"A bit better."},{"time":56834,"text":"I thought, the yo-yo\nis something for me to be good at."},{"time":60768,"text":"For the first time in my life,"},{"time":63499,"text":"I found my passion."},{"time":66856,"text":"I was spending all my time practicing."},{"time":69849,"text":"It took me hours and hours a day\nto build my skills up to the next level."}]},{"cues":[{"time":75348,"text":"And then, four years later,\nwhen I was 18 years old,"},{"time":80068,"text":"I was standing onstage\nat the World YoYo Contest."},{"time":83349,"text":"And I won."},{"time":84879,"text":"I was so excited."},{"time":86073,"text":"\"Yes, I did it! I became a hero."},{"time":88676,"text":"I may get many sponsors, a lot of money,"},{"time":91044,"text":"tons of interviews,\nand be on TV!\" I thought."}]},{"cues":[{"time":93854,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":95600,"text":"But after coming back to Japan,"},{"time":98844,"text":"totally nothing changed in my life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":101872,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":103607,"text":"I realized society\ndidn't value my passion."},{"time":108168,"text":"So I went back to my college"},{"time":110736,"text":"and became a typical Japanese worker\nas a systems engineer."},{"time":115244,"text":"I felt my passion,\nheart and soul, had left my body."},{"time":121575,"text":"I felt I was not alive anymore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":124394,"text":"So I started to consider what I should do,"},{"time":128320,"text":"and I thought, I wanted to make\nmy performance better,"},{"time":132920,"text":"and to show onstage\nhow spectacular the yo-yo could be"},{"time":137374,"text":"to change the public's image of the yo-yo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141521,"text":"So I quit my company"},{"time":144409,"text":"and started a career\nas a professional performer."},{"time":148399,"text":"I started to learn classic ballet,\njazz dance, acrobatics and other things"},{"time":153078,"text":"to make my performance better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155520,"text":"As a result of these efforts,\nand the help of many others,"},{"time":158696,"text":"it happened."},{"time":160956,"text":"I won the World YoYo Contest again\nin the artistic performance division."},{"time":165458,"text":"I passed an audition for Cirque Du Soleil."},{"time":168751,"text":"Today, I am standing on the TED stage"},{"time":172607,"text":"with the yo-yo in front of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":175190,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":179543,"text":"What I learned from the yo-yo is,"},{"time":182833,"text":"if I make enough effort with huge passion,"},{"time":187698,"text":"there is no impossible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190096,"text":"Could you let me share my passion with you"},{"time":192992,"text":"through my performance?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":194647,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":225997,"text":"(Water sound)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":232651,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":454790,"text":"(Music ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":457395,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":464602,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":543405,"text":"(Music ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":548177,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":570270,"text":"(Applause ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":573533,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":603738,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}